data.description: Are you an investor looking to add to your rental portfolio or a first-time homebuyer? Look no further than this quaint bungalow on Des Moines NE side. Relax in the living room and enjoy looking out the large bay window. The eat-kitchen is a great place to cook family meals. Laundry is on the main level. This home has two modest bedrooms and a full bath. The two-car detached garage is a great place to keep your vehicles out of the elements. The roof, mechanicals and windows are all newer. The assessor’s page has the basement listed as 362 square feet however this is not accurate. The basement is more like a crawlspace, only 50 feet and only accessible from the outside of the house. You are mere minutes from anything in the metro including all your daily amenities, Grandview Golf Course and downtown.
